OL,4,CDrug antidote spray already saving
OL,5,Clives in Wales
OL,6, A pilot to use a nasal spray to prevent
OL,7, heroin overdose deaths is now being
OL,8, rolled out across a Welsh police force.
OL,10,FNorth Wales Police says all officers
OL,11,Fcan now volunteer to carry the naloxone
OL,12,Fmedication.
OL,14,FIt follows a successful pilot in
OL,15,FFlintshire, where the antidote was used
OL,16,Fto save two lives.
OL,18,F"We need to do what we can to stop
OL,19,Fthese drug deaths," said the force's
OL,20,Foutgoing Police and Crime Commissioner,
OL,21,FArfon Jones.
